                    Apartment No. {!Booking__c.Unit_NumberFor__c} having Super Built up area {!Booking__c.Built_up_area__c}Sq.ft., and carpet area of {!Booking__c.Carpet_Area__c} Sq. m
                    (___ square feet), Balcony area {!Booking__c.Balcony_Area__c}Sq. m on {!Booking__c.Floor__c} floor {!Booking__c.Parking__c} space  along with {Booking__c.Undivided_Share_Of_Land__c} undivided share in the Schedule Property, in the Apartment 
                        building known as SOWPARNIKA PRANATHI.</div><br/><br/>
                    East by  : {!Booking__c.East_By__c}<br/>
                    West by  : {!Booking__c.West_By__c}<br/>
                    North by : {!Booking__c.North_By__c}<br/>
                    South by : {!Booking__c.South_By__c}<br/><br/><br/>
                </p>
                <p>
                  IN WITNESS WHEREOF the parties have signed this Agreement on the day month and year first above mentioned in the 
                    presence of the following witnesses.  
                </p>
                <p>
                    CONSENTING WITNESS:                                                       
Sowparnika Projects and Infrastructure Pvt. Ltd.,      

